PROCEDURE ShowInventory; FORWARD;
PROCEDURE DropItem; FORWARD;
PROCEDURE UseScroll; FORWARD;
PROCEDURE CastSpell; FORWARD;
PROCEDURE TeleportPlayerToFloor; FORWARD;
PROCEDURE ShowHelp; FORWARD;
